text: Nelly Wies-Weyrich (10 May 1933 - 5 July 2019) was a Luxembourgian archer. Wies-Weyrich competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics.Nelly Wies-WeyrichNelly WIES-WEYRICH == References == Category:1933 births Category:2019 deaths Category:Luxembourgian archers Category:Olympians for Luxembourg
